Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然是那種又年輕又可愛的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可沒有聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母親大人是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和真白並不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 雖然我一開始也無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過如果那些人是普通人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅就沒辦法得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我無論怎麼感謝都覺得不夠呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
